TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers=1;

$a1=non_zero_random(-10, 10);
$b1=non_zero_random(-10, 10);
$c=random(2, 20);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
The vertical asymptote of the curve
 \[   y=\frac{$a1 x^3}{x +$b1} \]
is given by \( x=\) \{ans_rule(20)\} $BR
